data.description: Sought after gated neighborhood of Lake Marianna Reserve in beautiful Auburndale Florida! This 4 bedroom, 3 bath home has a tasteful color pallet ready for new owners to make it their own. Why build when you can move now as the owners are motivated!! The master bedroom features a large walk-in closet and glamorous en-suite bathroom with a large soaking tub, dual sinks and a seperate shower stall. The 4th bedroom with private bath is perfect to be used as an in law suite or for older children who prefer more privacy if needed. The heart of this home is the kitchen with solid surface counter tops, stainless steel appliances, breakfast nook and a water filtration system with an osmosis faucet providing that open concept feel that’s great for entertaining guests. Additional rooms to be noted are the breakfast nook and the separate office perfect for the virtual worker or it could be used in a multitude of other ways such as a playroom, 5th bedroom or sitting area. This home features a level lot with fenced yard. The home also features a separate electrical box for a generator set up, making it easy to switch over when the power goes out; ideal for Florida’s hurricane season! Gated Community with a community dock on Lake Mariana, Boat Ramp, Playground, Basketball court, and Low HOA. This home is conveniently located near I-4 making an easy commute to Orlando or Tampa, medical offices, restaurants, shopping and schools.
